name: Much Anger In Him (V)
Lore: '''Adventure, heh. Excitement, heh. A Jedi craves not these things. You are reckless.''',
Text: 'Use 4 Force to deploy on opponent''s non-droid, non-Jedi Master character (or 2 Force on a Rebel). Character''s game text is canceled and they draw one battle destiny if unable to otherwise. Opponent may lose three cards from hand (may not be reduced) to cancel this Effect.',
